					<h1 class="solo">Results &amp; Testimonials</h1>
					<div class="c1">
						<p>Perhaps the ideal way to decide if College Works Painting is the best choice is to get the story in words and pictures, from the people who matter most: our many satisfied customers and the entrepreneurs who did the job. Click here to see our gallery of results.</p>
					</div>
