						<h3>Get It Straight from the Source</h3>
	
						<p>Most were confident going in, others cautiously optimistic. But they all had one thing in common. Once they met our energetic, enterprising interns, heard our story, learned about our guarantee and checked out our references, they forged right ahead. And after they stepped back to admire the job there was no doubt: College Works Painting delivers beautiful results, and gives undergrads a beautiful once-in-a-lifetime opportunity. Just look!</p>
