						<h2>Customer Testimonials</h2>
						<blockquote>
							<p>Our experience with the company and the workers, Marc Blumenthal, being on the team was very positive. After the job was efficiently completed the appearance of our house was so clean and the curb appeal set it apart from other houses on the block.  We highly recommend the work of Marc for your next painting project.</p>
							<p class="small">Mr. and Mrs. David Barksdale <em>(Golden Valley, MN)</em></p>
						</blockquote>
						<blockquote>
							<p>Throughout the job I was extremely pleased with Sarah's leadership and attention to detail. She was on the job, fully engaged every step of the way. I had a quite a bit of work done on my two story home, and I was no easy job. Her crew was very pleasant and courteous, and worked very hard to completion.</p>
							
							<p>I give Sarah and College Works a full recommendation to anyone looking for a quality paint job.</p>
							<p class="small">Dianne Martin <em>(Harrisburg, PA)</em></p>
						</blockquote>
						<blockquote>
							<p>Today your crew finished the paint job at my house. Everything I asked for was delivered. I enjoyed working with you and appreciated your willingness and flexibility. The painters you hired knew what they were doing and did a good job.</p>
							<p class="small">Joy Lucke <em>(Austin, TX)</em></p>
						</blockquote>
